Package controller

Class InsideAlbumController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.InsideAlbumController
  • public class InsideAlbumController
extends java.lang.Object
    The InsideAlbumController class is responsible for handling user interactions for the scene insideAlbum (insideAlbum.fxml). This scene occurs when the user clicks "open album".
    Author:
    Vincent Phung, William McFarland
